      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended primarily for those looking for a major project or a source for parts. The body has significant rust, particularly around the wheel wells and undercarriage, and the paint is heavily oxidized and peeling. Mechanically, the car requires substantial work to be roadworthy, including engine repairs and a complete suspension overhaul. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and some missing trim pieces. It is being sold strictly as-is.",
