    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine has a noticeable knock and the transmission slips between gears, suggesting a need for major repairs or a total overhaul. Externally, there is heavy rust on the rocker panels and the clear coat is peeling extensively across most surfaces. The interior shows heavy wear, including several tears in the upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This is a project car sold as-is for someone with the tools and time to restore it.",
