      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly fixer-upper? This vehicle is looking for a new home and a little TLC! While it currently has significant wear and tear and will need some mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back to its best, it's a fantastic opportunity for a mechanic or a DIY enthusiast to roll up their sleeves and bring it back to life!",
