    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty \u2013 it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such incredible care of it, you won't find a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh new car smell. Honestly, it's in pristine, showroom-ready shape and just waiting for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin, you're going to fall in love! \u2728",
