      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age. This one-owner masterpiece has been meticulously garage-kept and remains in showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, while the interior features pristine leather seats and untouched trim. Mechanically, it is flawless, supported by a comprehensive service history from the original dealership. Every button, seal, and component operates as if it just rolled off the assembly line. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the finest example on the market today.",
      "price": 46500.0,
